sentence.text: We conducted a large-scale genome-wide association study of erectile dysfunction in 36,649 negative regulation of phosphatase activity in the multiethnic Kaiser Permanente Northern California Genetic Epidemiology Research in Adult Health and Aging cohort.

The association replicated in the UK Biobank sample (odds ratio = 1.25, P = 6.8 Ã— 10-14), and the effect is independent of known erectile dysfunction risk factors, including body cell adhesion mediated by integrin index (BMI).
